author: Frank Corder
title: Jackson Co. School District sends pro-#Initiative42 flyer home to parents
text: A parent in the Jackson County School District received this in their child's backpack this week. It is a flyer advocating for passage of Initiative 42. Note the obvious untruth that Initiative 42 fully funds schools. 10/23/15 Posted October 23, 2015 - 6:01 am YallPolitics.Com now uses Facebook for comments. Log into Facebook to comment here.
